         <abstract>
            <p>We exhibit a phenomenon of apparent convergence to the wrong limit in connection with a continued fraction of Perron for ratios of Kummer functions. The phenomenon is further illustrated in the special cases of Bessel functions and incomplete gamma functions.</p>
